name: get state
handle notify data
func:
var New = {appID:null, category:null, data:null, unit:null};
New.appID = msg.payload.obj.str[0].$.val
New.category = msg.payload.obj.str[1].$.val
New.data = msg.payload.obj.str[2].$.val 
New.unit = msg.payload.obj.str[3].$.val
msg.payload = New
return msg;

return msg;
